description:
Applicability
This schedule must be used in combination with. FO Farm Service - Irrigation Pumping (on Season). This schedule applies to: 1) pumping of subsurface water for drainage or irrigation which is not eligible to be served with electricity sold to the District by the City and County of San Francisco pursuant to Section 9(l) of the Federal Raker Act; or 2) pumping from natural waterways or District facilities. This schedule is applicable on an annual basis only.
On Season:
Connected Load Charge, per HP: $ 3.00
Energy Charge per kWh $ 0.1061
Off Season:
Energy Charge, per kWh $ 0.2002
name: Schedule FO Farm Service - Irrigation Pumping(off Season)
